		<body>
			<pb n="1"/>
				<p rend="align(right)"><placeName>N York</placeName> <date>17<hi rend="sup">th</hi> Feby&#47;61</date>.</p>
				<p><addressee>Rev. I. Leeser</addressee> <placeName>Pha</placeName></p>
			<p rend="indent(1)">Rev Dr Sir</p>
			<p rend="indent(2)">The bearer <persName>R&#39;. Abraham<lb/> Nissan</persName> is come among us to plead the<lb/> cause of our starving brethren at<lb/> <placeName>Jerusalem</placeName>.  At no time neither the<lb/> memory of man has their condition<lb/> been so pitiable as at present&#44; and<lb/> especially in the community which<lb/> he particularly represents&#44; the<lb/> Ashkenazin Jerooshim.</p>
			<p rend="indent(1)">As he asks for nothing for<lb/> himself&#44; but that every donation be<lb/> sent to <placeName>Jerusalem</placeName> direct&#44; I trust<lb/> you will afford his mission your<lb/> powerful support&#44; as well by your<lb/> exertions among your friends as in<lb/> the columns of the Occident.</p>
			<p rend="indent(1)">I am Rev. Dr Sir</p>
			<p rend="indent(2)">Very respectfully</p>
			<p rend="indent(3)"><persName role="author">MJRaphall</persName></p>
			<pb n="2"/>
				<p><hi rend="bold">Buxlorf</hi></p>
		</body>
